DerivedStateOf			: convert one or multiple state objects into another state
DisposableEffect		: effects that require cleanup, For side effects that need to be cleaned up after the keys change or if the composable leaves the Composition, use DisposableEffect. 
rememberCoroutineScope	: obtain a composition-aware scope to launch a coroutine outside a composable
rememberUpdatedState	: reference a value in an effect that shouldn't restart if the value changes
SideEffect				: publish Compose state to non-compose code
snapshotFlow			: convert Compose's State into Flows
produceState			: convert non-Compose state into Compose state
LaunchedEffect 			: run suspend functions in the scope of a composable
	
2(DRS) PL

